( <i>piano plays</i> )

01:04.163 --> 01:06.731
¶ Making your way           
      in the world today ¶

01:06.765 --> 01:09.801
¶ Takes everything you've got

01:09.835 --> 01:12.637
¶ Taking a break        
    from all your worries ¶

01:12.671 --> 01:15.740
¶ Sure would help a lot

01:15.774 --> 01:21.178
¶ Wouldn't you like       
         to get away? ¶

01:21.213 --> 01:23.865
¶ Sometimes you want to go

01:23.899 --> 01:28.753
